BUDDHA BOY was bumped nearing the first turn, chased the pace two wide around the first turn then retreated inside around the far turn. DOMI was bumped at the start, tracked the pace four and five wide and faltered nearing the quarter pole.

HARLAN'S LEGACY tracked in the three path around the first turn and was in the four path down the backstretch, was coaxed in the three path around the far turn and tipped out to the five path into the stretch, but was empty.
